headline: Paycom Tops Ranking for Company Culture, Compensation
summary: OKLAHOMA CITY, December 13, 2024--Paycom Software, Inc. (NYSE: PAYC) ("Paycom"), a leading provider of comprehensive, cloud-based human capital management software, ranked in the top 10 for Best Company Culture, Best Compensation and Best CEO in awards from Comparably, an employee review and salary platform.

headline: Texas’ Jahdae Barron Named 2024 Paycom Jim Thorpe Award Winner
summary: OKLAHOMA CITY, December 13, 2024--As the leader of the No. 1 pass defense team in the country, The University of Texas at Austin’s Jahdae Barron has been named the 2024 Paycom Jim Thorpe Award Winner. The announcement was made live tonight on The Home Depot College Football Awards on ESPN.
